name: Phillip Andremarine
description: I am a happy type of person. A kind and generous to those who are good to me. I can also consider myself as a thoughtful and understanding woman, willing to mingle, friendly, and easy to be with. Love is a great feeling for me that can inspire and make me feel energized. I am optimistic and fun-loving person too. To add, I work hard to be able to do my responsibilities towards my family and be able to live this life. Yet, I have the courage to fight the difficulties that I am facing everyday. I am ready for love and I want it to happen.
